      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n\t<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n\t<style>\n\t\t:root { --frame-color: {{frameColor}}; }\n\t\tbody { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: transparent; width: {{frameWidth}}px; height: {{frameHeight}}px; overflow: hidden; }\n\t\t.neon-frame { position: relative; width: {{frameWidth}}px; height: {{frameHeight}}px; background: transparent; border-radius: 8px; }\n\t\t.neon-border { position: absolute; inset: -2px; border-radius: 10px; padding: 2px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--frame-color), transparent, var(--frame-color), transparent); background-size: 300% 300%; -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0); -webkit-mask-composite: xor; mask-composite: exclude; animation: frameRotate {{animSpeed}}s linear infinite; }\n\t\t.node-corner { position: absolute; width: {{nodeSize}}px; height: {{nodeSize}}px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 12px #fff, 0 0 24px var(--frame-color); animation: nodePulse {{pulseSpeed}}s infinite ease-in-out; }\n\t\t.node-tl { top: {{nodeOffset}}px; left: {{nodeOffset}}px; animation-delay: 0s; }\n\t\t.node-tr { top: {{nodeOffset}}px; right: {{nodeOffset}}px; animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n\t\t.node-bl { bottom: {{nodeOffset}}px; left: {{nodeOffset}}px; animation-delay: 0.6s; }\n\t\t.node-br { bottom: {{nodeOffset}}px; right: {{nodeOffset}}px; animation-delay: 0.9s; }\n\t\t@keyframes frameRotate { 0% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 50% { background-position: 100% 50%; } 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; } }\n\t\t@keyframes nodePulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } 50% { transform: scale(1.6); opacity: 0.7; } }\n\t</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\t<div class=\"neon-frame\">\n\t\t<div class=\"neon-border\"></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"node-corner node-tl\"></div><div class=\"node-corner node-tr\"></div><div class=\"node-corner node-bl\"></div><div class=\"node-corner node-br\"></div>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html>"
